1.title: SpongeBob in Paranormal Activity 4
1.plot: Welcome back to the house. The fun is just about to start. After strange experiences, the gang must acquire the help of Mr. Krabs who isn't happy with Bob and Squid since they quit the Krusty Krab. What will happen next in this Season 2 premier?

2.title: SpobgeBob in Paranormal Activity 5
2.plot: Locked in, no power. What's going on? What's the gang gonna do? And Yakon isn't working alone? So many questions are answered while some many more are asked in Part 5 to The Paranormal Activity Series. Only one more episode to go.

3.title: SpobgeBob in Paranormal Activity 6: The Finale
3.plot: Total Plot Line UNKOWN: DoodleBob casts the gang into oblivion to be tormented the way he was in Hell, aided by his magic pencil. What will the gang do to get out of this one?

1.title: SpobgeBob in Paranormal Activity
1.plot: A monster is terrorizing SpongeBob and Patrick at their house. they decided to record the whole thing to find a way to stop him...!.

2.title: SpongeBob in Paranormal Activity 2
2.plot: The monster is is still haunting SpongeBob and Patrick's house, so they decide to call an expert...Squidward.

3.title: SpongeBob in Paranormal Activity 3
3.plot: The monster is still alive!!. Spongebob and Patrick will try anything just to get rid of him!.. this time with Sandy's help.

imdb.plot outline: SpongeBob and Patrick have moved into a new house outside of Bikini Bottom. Only problem is the house is haunted by a sexual demon named Yakon. In this 6 episode adventure, SpongeBob and Patrick must get help from Squidward Tentacles: Demonologist, Sandy Cheeks: Explosives Expert and Mr. Eugene Krabs: Professional Ghost Hunterto defeat Yakon and his boss to save themselves and their home. Can they survive?.
